Desktop or Web application

Three functionalities
 * City creator
 * City explorer
 * City comparer and suggester

City Creator
 * Create from scrath or template, sandbox style
 * Map creator, infrastructure layout
 * City parameters, auto generate map and infrastructure layout

City Explorer
 * Explore existing cities
 * Cities you have made
 * Share cities you make with friends

City Comparer
 * Find a city that matches your preferencs
 * Compare attributes of cities, diversity, economy, social scene, etc.
